# SQL Sales Analysis

## Overview

Performed sales data analysis using SQL queries to identify revenue trends, top-performing products, customer behavior, and business performance metrics.

## Tools Used

- SQL
- MySQL / PostgreSQL
- Joins
- Aggregate Functions
- CTEs
- Window Functions

## Skills Demonstrated

- Data Extraction
- Data Cleaning
- Query Optimization
- Business Analysis
- KPI Reporting

## Key Analysis

- Total Revenue Analysis
- Top Selling Products
- Customer Purchase Behavior
- Regional Sales Performance
- Monthly Sales Trends

## Files

- SQL_Queries.sql
- Project_Report.pdf
